ram Poindexter Maury|Abram P. Maury]] (AJ)\n* {{ushr|Tennessee|9|9}}. [[James K. Polk]] (J)\n* {{ushr|Tennessee|10|10}}. [[Ebenezer J. Shields]] (AJ)\n* {{ushr|Tennessee|11|11}}. [[Cave Johnson]] (J)\n* {{ushr|Tennessee|12|12}}. [[Adam Huntsman]] (J)\n* {{ushr|Tennessee|13|13}}. [[William Claiborne Dunlap|William C. Dunlap]] (J)\n\n==== [[List of United States Representatives from Vermont|Vermont]] ====\n* {{ushr|Vermont|1|1}}. [[Hiland Hall]] (AJ)\n* {{ushr|Vermont|2|2}}. [[William Slade]] (AM)\n* {{ushr|Vermont|3|3}}. [[Horace Everett]] (AJ)\n* {{ushr|Vermont|4|4}}. [[Heman Allen (Milton)|Heman Allen]] (AJ)\n* {{ushr|Vermont|5|5}}. [[Henry F. Janes]] (AM)\n\n==== [[List of United States Representatives from Virginia|Virginia]] ====\n* {{ushr|Virginia|1|1}}. [[George Loyall]] (J)\n* {{ushr|Virginia|2|2}}. [[John Y. Mason]] (J), until January 11, 1837\n* {{ushr|Virginia|3|3}}. [[John Winston Jones|John W. Jones]] (J)\n* {{ushr|Virginia|4|4}}. [[George Dromgoole|George C. Dromgoole]] (J)\n* {{ushr|Virginia|5|5}}. [[James W. Bouldin]] (J)\n* {{ushr|Virginia|6|6}}. [[Walter Coles]] (J)\n* {{ushr|Virginia|7|7}}. [[Nathaniel Claiborne|Nathaniel H. Claiborne]] (AJ)\n* {{ushr|Virginia|8|8}}. [[Henry A. Wise]] (J)\n* {{ushr|Virginia|9|9}}. [[John Roane]] (J)\n* {{ushr|Virginia|10|10}}. [[John Taliaferro]] (AJ)\n* {{ushr|Virginia|11|11}}. [[John Robertson (congressman)|John Robertson]] (AJ)\n* {{ushr|Virginia|12|12}}. [[James Garland (Virginia politician)|James Garland]] (J)\n* {{ushr|Virginia|13|13}}. [[John M. Patton]] (J)\n* {{ushr|Virginia|14|14}}. [[Charles F. Mercer]] (AJ)\n* {{ushr|Virginia|15|15}}. [[Edward Lucas (congressman)|Edward Lucas]] (J)\n* {{ushr|Virginia|16|16}}. [[James M. H. Beale]] (J)\n* {{ushr|Virginia|17|17}}. [[Robert Craig (representative)|Robert Craig]] (J)\n* {{ushr|Virginia|18|18}}. [[George Washington Hopkins|George W. Hopkins]] (J)\n* {{ushr|Virginia|19|19}}. [[William McComas]] (AJ)\n* {{ushr|Virginia|20|20}}. [[Joseph Johnson (Virginia politi