eb |url=https://millercenter.org/president/pierce/campaigns-and-elections |title=Franklin Pierce: Campaigns and Elections |last=Baker |first=Jean H. |date=October 4, 2016 |website=Miller Center: US |publisher=University of Virginia |location=Charlottesville, VA}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"12Aj5\">{{cite book |last=Richardson |first=James D. |date=1903 |title=A Compilation of the Messages and Papers of the Presidents |volume=V |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=dUQzAQAAMAAJ&pg=PA305 |location=Washington, DC |publisher=Bureau of National Literature and Art |pages=305\u2013306 |author-link=James D. Richardson}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"8dv1j\">{{cite web |title=Winfield Scott |url=https://www.nps.gov/people/winfield-scott.htm |publisher=National Park Service |accessdate=January 25, 2019}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"4PNmt\">{{cite magazine |last1=Malanga |first1=Steven |title=The War Hero New York Forgot |url=https://www.city-journal.org/html/war-hero-new-york-forgot-13612.html |accessdate=January 25, 2019 |magazine=City Journal |date=2013}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"7TErp\">''Fanny J. Crosby: An Autobiography'' ([[Peabody, Massachusetts]]: Hendrickson Publishers Marketing, 2013 printing), p. 88, {{ISBN|978-1-59856-281-1}}.</ref>\n<ref name=\"XTEwe\">{{cite book |last=Ramey |first=Sanford |date=1885 |title=Kings of the Battle-field |url=https://archive.org/details/kingsofbattlefie00rameuoft |location= Philadelphia, PA |publisher=Aetna Publishing Company |page=[https://archive.org/details/kingsofbattlefie00rameuoft/page/356 356]}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"mlNaU\">''The Origin of Certain Place Names in the United States'' by Henry Gannett</ref>\n<ref name=\"lxtym\">{{cite book|last=Kenny|first=Hamill|title=West Virginia Place Names: Their Origin and Meaning, Including the Nomenclature of the Streams and Mountains|url=https://babel.hathitrust.org/cgi/pt?id=mdp.39015009099824;view=1up;seq=709;size=125|year=1945|publisher=The Place Name Press|location=Piedmont, WV|page=685}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"5MJvB\">[h